	* move.c: For large fields use 'cob_decimal_setget_fld'
	* numeric.c: Added support for large BINARY/COMP-X/COMP-N 
	* termio.c: Updated 'bin_digits' table for larger fields
	* common.h: Removed  define  COB_MAX_COMPX

