	* screenio.c: fixed compiler warnings related to get_crt3_status

2022-11-10  Ron Norman <rjn@inglenet.com>

	* fileio.c: Preliminary implemenation of support for the
	  COB_FILENAME_SPACES option (default TRUE, checking option to disable).
	  If the name in ASSIGN variable starts with double quote then
	  trailing spaces are included in file name 
	  If the name in ASSIGN variable has invalid data status 9/004

