	* fbdb.c: manual merge of fileio.c from 2019-08-25 and 2021-01-08
	  including clean-up and bugfix of that
	* fbdb.c: for retry lock: only set loc object dbt once,
	* screenio.c (cob_get_color_pair, cob_screen_init): fix overflow
	  when COLOR_PAIRS is bigger than SHRT_MAX
