2021-02-17  Ron Norman <rjn@inglenet.com>

	* fsqlxfd.c: If PIC 9 field in index had HIGH-VALUES set to all 9s
				cob_index_to_xfd is now passed 'cond' which 
				if COB_FI will set the index fields to lowest value and 
				if COB_LA will set the index fields to highest value
	* common.c: Add  'cob_get_env' to check for 'envname' then 'COB_envname'
	* fileio.c: Changed to use cob_get_env
