	* common.h: Additional flags added to cob_file for commit/rollback
	* fileio.c: Numerous changes to support commit/rollback for all files
	* fileio.h: 'gentable' removed as table is created if not present
	* foci.c: Fix to set TIME and TIMESTAMP column types
	* fodbc.c: Fix to set TIME and TIMESTAMP column types
	* fsqlxfd.c: Removed check for 'gentable'

