	* fileio.c: Added a flag 'config' to the table of I/O modules
	            so that it is now which ones had been configured 
	* fisam.c: Additional work for ISAM logging/transaction ability
	           VBISAM 2.2 in default and C-ISAM mode works fine
	           D-ISAM 7.2 is also working in transaction mode

2021-01-10  Ron Norman <rjn@inglenet.com> 

	* fisam.c: Additional work for ISAM logging/transaction ability
	           VBISAM 2.2 in default and C-ISAM mode works fine
	           D-ISAM 7.0 is not working in transaction mode
	           and it may be that D-ISAM 7.2 or better is required

