2020-02-27  Simon Sobisch <simonsobisch@gnu.org>

	* common.h: definition of COB_A_NORETURN for newer HPUX (__HP_cc)

2020-02-15  Ron Norman <rjn@inglenet.com>

	* common.h, fileio.c, fileio.h, foci.c, fodbc.c, fsqlxfd.c:
		Updates to support RELATIVE file for processing by
		the OCI/ODBC I/O modules.
		A 'RELATIVE" table has a column called 'rid_tablename'
		which is PRIMARY KEY.
		As much code as possible was moved into fileio.c to
		manage the logical 'record number' so that foci.c & fodbc.c
		do not need to duplicate that logic

