	* common.h (cob_field): Field 'size' moved from 'cob_field_desc'.
	  (COB_FIELD_SIZE, COB_FIELD_DATA): Removed.
	* common.c, fileio.c, move.c, numeric.c, strings.c, termio.c: Updated.

